_sText: A small villa built somewhere on a small rock spire in the ocean. You can access the villa which contains 3 floors and the roof, go around it or use a small path below the villa, round the rock column.. Still the map size is quite small so there will me much action!!! Recommended players: ANY (2-24) Enjoy! ***Hint: This map is also available as "fy" map on my homepage. (You can switch between English and German by clicking the icons in the navigation bar.) ***Hint: There are no isles or sth and no decals ON PURPOSE.
